<div class="hidden" data-skip-type="pass">
  <h5>You can pass without penalty:</h5>
  <button class="pass-button" data-action="click->turn#skip">NEXT</button>
</div>

<div class="hidden" data-skip-type="skip">
  <h5>You can skip the words but lose a point:</h5>
  <button class="skip-button" data-action="click->turn#skip">SKIP (-1)</button>
</div>

<div class="hidden" data-skip-type="bonk">
  <h5>Bonk the player if they broke the rules:</h5>
  <button class="skip-button" data-action="click->turn#skip" data-turn-skip-param="bonk">BONK!</button>
</div>
